          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"key-insights\">Key Insights</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>2017 was the costliest year, dominated by Hurricane Maria devastating Dominica and Caribbean islands</li>\n<li>The 2004 Indian Ocean tsunami caused massive economic damage across multiple small island nations</li>\n<li>Small island states suffer disproportionately -- damages often exceed 100% of their GDP</li>\n<li>The trend shows increasing economic damages over time as more assets are exposed to natural hazards</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
